    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless with a glass-like finish, and the interior retains its original factory scent with no signs of wear on the leather or trim. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the dealership, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a truly pristine example of this model.",
