      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine struggles to maintain a steady idle and requires significant mechanical work to be roadworthy, and the transmission shifts harshly. Cosmetically, the exterior has several large dents and peeling clear coat, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and missing trim pieces. It is being sold as-is, and towing is recommended for transport.",
