    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or dent\u2014it's basically brand new. If you're looking for perfection without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
