      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless factory finish with no swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. The interior is pristine; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the cabin retains its original new-car scent. Mechanically, it is turn-key and absolute perfection, supported by a comprehensive folder of every service record since day one. No modifications, no stories\u2014just a pure, untouched example for the discerning enthusiast who demands the best. All original keys, manuals, and the original window sticker are included.",
